    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>"We expect that Ethiopia will be a really democratic country, united not by force of arms but by the freely expressed will of the people involved." -- Meles Zenawi, the head of the rebel group that has taken over in the capital of Ethiopia.  [ A6:4. ]</p>
      </block>
